        <h3>The Fix: Critical Section / Queueing</h3>
        <p>The corrected version solves this by ensuring that all updates to the shared <code>correctedProgressPercentage</code> variable happen in a controlled, sequential manner. This is achieved using a simple queue and a processing flag:</p>
